=-3+\\frac{1}{1-x}$ ，\n根据反比例函数 $y=\\frac{1}{-x}$ 的平移可得到 $f(x)$ ，则此时 $f(x)$ 单调递增, 作出图像如下图所示,\n\n第二步:\n令\n\n$$\ng(x)=f(x)-m x+\\frac{2}{3} m=0\n$$\n\n即\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_10_24_47a253f79e08acf28419g-26.jpg?height=429&width=577&top_left_y=314&top_left_x=1342","line":523}],"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"8afkgc","at":1771470889212}},"smart_blocks:20-Product/01-数学教学/试卷/10-试卷汇总/功底考/功底考16题1-16套.md#科目二答题示例": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.03525844,0.00758808,0.04889606,-0.0862542,-0.00346662,0.02231758,-0.0004067,0.01371396,0.01272749,-0.00356764,0.0164808,-0.06051467,0.04528381,0.01312361,0.01271295,0.00068384,0.04966303,-0.02417588,-0.07529695,-0.01811758,0.14847371,-0.04060118,-0.01139485,-0.05046431,0.07456374,0.02742649,0.02491658,-0.01777627,0.00449861,-0.18463418,-0.00137395,0.0131364,0.00821683,0.03282926,0.03514289,-0.05070892,-0.01812538,0.04122939,-0.07290513,0.00946253,-0.01110673,0.08668356,0.03457341,-0.03206849,0.04462155,-0.01980193,-0.04934308,-0.04752627,0.03252728,-0.00329633,-0.05976976,-0.0003002,-0.01048085,0.02737167,-0.01260993,0.00250244,-0.01301982,0.06053251,0.01431419,-0.00314412,0.04750811,-0.00428194,-0.20811728,0.01450801,0.06086013,-0.01773691,-0.00785423,-0.02799143,0.06300388,0.10506669,-0.02434628,0.00043655,-0.0014136,0.03302015,0.01237372,0.01745796,0.02010514,-0.02564015,-0.05074188,-0.05237545,-0.00718755,0.07498208,0.02837949,0.01447117,0.00402368,0.02167262,-0.00164772,-0.0609751,0.00871315,-0.06176384,-0.00989307,-0.0171866,0.00285301,0.0306621,-0.03766954,0.00100695,0.01725139,0.03528572,-0.02385794,0.11471247,-0.04426514,0.08271465,0.01327654,-0.09246568,-0.00530264,-0.06441155,-0.04486443,-0.05762672,-0.02697159,-0.01298506,0.00936953,-0.03666092,0.0518488,-0.08187363,-0.00582315,-0.01064737,0.05569132,0.03169432,-0.00321305,-0.00157912,0.03122104,0.06276559,0.03382426,-0.06541278,-0.03953328,-0.0680952,0.04031891,0.00653158,0.0